<br>
<br>
I came here at 39 and stayed till 44.  Great XP  Great Loot.  Here is the story<br>
<br>
The dreadland cave you want is the very NW corner of the zone.  Many people will run in there, thinking its the entrance to Lost Valley....just invis them and levitate them and send them southward and they will be grateful.<br>
<br>
This is how i did it.<br>
<br>
Make 39 Fire Pet. (focused)<br>
Give it Phantom Chain, 2 dagger symbols, coldstone and elemental defender.  Then Burn out 2<br>
<br>
You will get hit pulling for your pet, so cast GS and PC on yourself.<br>
<br>
Park yourself about 3 seconds worth of a run from alcove with 1st yeti.  Tell pet to guard here.  <br>
<br>
All you need on your spell gems is Blaze and Shock of Flame.  You pull with SoF....anything else and your pet wont be able to taunt mob off you and youll get beaten to a bloody pulp.<br>
<br>
1. Search for Wanderer. This yeti is a rare spawn...but if he is present in cave, he will be on a 16 min timer.  If he is not in cave, be alert.  He will pop at the worst possible time and become an add.<br>
<br>
2. Take out the Alcove with the 1st yeti in it.  Stand far back and cast SoF on it.  Run to pet and then sick pet.  MED untill Ganer pierces the yeti to 70% health, and chain nuke Blaze.  2 outta do it.  <br>
<br>
<br>
See how easy that was?<br>
<br>
When your pet walks back to guard position...run to the cave on the right with 3 yetis in it.  SoF the yeti on the LEFT or you will get adds.  Run to pet and sick Ganer on it.  2 Blazes from 70% health is all you need.  <br>
<br>
The Yetis have very little resistance, so expect your spells to hit for max<br>
<br>
Continue to clear out the right cave and proceed to the other cave.  All the Yetis are on a 21 min timer.  Kill all 7, then take a 21 min break and clean your house, change oil, wash the dog..etc<br>
<br>
Here is how many yetis i killed before i leveled (i kept track of it)<br>
<br>
Lvl 39  45<br>
Lvl 40  55<br>
Lvl 41  65<br>
Lvl 42 75<br>
Lvl 43 90 <br>
<br>
<br>
I did all of this in 2 12 hour marathons and 1 8 hour marathon.   I came away with gems, coin, words, runes, and flowers to give your EQ wife.  All in All i made about 3k.  Now i can buy my Coldain Boots   )<br>
<br>
If the  Roaming Yeti is present...be alert.  Wait till he walks away from ALL 3 caves..thats when you attack to assure no adds.<br>
<br>
Good luck Mages, but you wont need it here<br>
<br>
Hope this Helps<br>
<br>
